  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the starting price for The Terraces at Estate 361?",
      "answer": "The Terraces at Estate 361 starts at ₹2.40 Cr onwards for 1.5 BHK residences. Prices vary by unit type, floor, and preferred location charges (PLC). GST is additional."
    },
    {
      "question": "Where is The Terraces at Estate 361 located?",
      "answer": "The project is located in Sector 36A, Gurugram, on the Dwarka Expressway — at the confluence of the Dwarka Expressway, the proposed Metro corridor, and the Central Peripheral Road. It is adjacent to the planned Global City CBD."
    },
    {
      "question": "What configurations are available at The Terraces?",
      "answer": "The Terraces offers 1.5 BHK residences (1,144 sq ft total area), 2 BHK residences (1,565 sq ft), and 2 BHK Duplex Loft units (1,687 sq ft). All units have 2 bathrooms."
    },
    {
      "question": "Is The Terraces at Estate 361 RERA registered?",
      "answer": "Yes. The Terraces at Estate 361 is registered with HARERA under registration number RC/REP/HARERA/GGM/1012/744/2025/115. Details are available at haryanarera.gov.in."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the IGBC Platinum certification for The Terraces?",
      "answer": "The Terraces is IGBC Platinum Pre-Certified, the highest rating by the Indian Green Building Council. This covers climate-responsive architecture, VRF air-conditioning, energy-efficient water heating, rainwater harvesting, solar rooftop systems, and STP."
    },
    {
      "question": "What are the exclusive community terraces at this project?",
      "answer": "The Terraces has 8 resident-only community spaces spread across 5,000 sq ft at different levels within the tower — a rock climbing zone, yoga deck, zen garden, tropical garden, cactus garden, herb garden, farm-to-table kitchen, and kids lounge."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the Treated Fresh Air system in each home?",
      "answer": "Every residence is equipped with a Treated Fresh Air (TFA) system that continuously supplies filtered, conditioned, and dehumidified outdoor air, designed to maintain indoor AQI between 0 and 50 as per WELL guidelines."
    },
    {
      "question": "Who is the developer of The Terraces at Estate 361?",
      "answer": "The developer is Max Estates Limited, the real estate arm of Max Group — a multi-business conglomerate founded in 1982. Max Estates has delivered Grade A commercial properties including Max Towers, Max Square, and Max House, all at 100% occupancy."
    },
    {
      "question": "What wellness facilities are available at The Terraces?",
      "answer": "The estate includes an integrated on-site wellness centre with next-generation health diagnostics, light medical therapies, ayurveda, acupuncture, cold plunges, infrared saunas, and pranic healing. Care at Home services are managed by Antara Senior Living."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the payment plan for The Terraces at Estate 361?",
      "answer": "The payment plan is structured around construction milestones: 10% on application, 10% within 90 days of application, 20% on ground floor casting, 20% on 18th floor casting, and 40% on possession."
    }
  ],
